             was indicted for <rs id="t18170416-165-off866" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170416-165-off866" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170416-165-off866" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18170416-165-cd867" type="crimeDate">28th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-165-off866 t18170416-165-cd867"></join>, four glass cruets, value 6s., and four cruet-tops, value 4s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18170416-165-victim1265" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Smith
                  <interp inst="t18170416-165-victim1265" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
